Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:13.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:21.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:43.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you just say,\NCaptain Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:45.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:49.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As you heard.\NDon't make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:54.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia Kuchiki is guilty of\Na first-degree offense
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:02:01.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and will be executed in 25 days at\Nthe Central Execution Grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:06.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is the final decision\Nof the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:14.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the last time\Nwe exchange words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, the next time I see you\Nwill be at the execution stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:32.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We shall not shed tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:36.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For tears mean the defeat\Nof the body to the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:45.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And to us, that simply proves that\Nthe existence of a heart is a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:54.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lesson Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shattered Shaft!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:03:01.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the bottom of the Shattered Shaft,\Nyou have 72 hours, or three days,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:05.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,before the chain is\Ncompletely Encroached.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:10.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must come back up here\Nas a Soul Reaper before the time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:14.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, we'll have to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:17.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the Hollow that you become.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!\NYou intend to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:26.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes...when you give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:42.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Completely hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:43.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh?!\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:48.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I will never be able to\Nlet you enter the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:56.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you are able to activate\Nyour powers at will,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:04:00.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you will die a dog's death\Nin the Soul Society!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:03.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:06.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember the first time\Nyou used it and retrace those steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:11.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier said than done.\NI was so desperate that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What were you so desperate about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:15.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:19.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A person takes a sword when\Nhe's trying to protect something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:29.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's your life, social status,\Nreputation... loved ones, beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though the motives might differ,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there's no difference in\Nthe desire to protect something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:38.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Think back. What were you\Ntrying to protect back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:40.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:47.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was...trying to protect\NIchigo's kid sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:49.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A red cap...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,long hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And since she's Ichigo's sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:05:00.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like Ichigo... a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:02.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you failed at remembering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:12.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:18.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:35.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was so desperate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So desperate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:47.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It shined!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:04.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When you need us,\Ndon't hesitate, just call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:11.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation...\Nwhy would you need us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:17.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry. I remembered\Nall kinds of things and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:23.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't even in danger,\Nyet you called us! You terrible hussy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki... stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts when you kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm pissed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:34.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– You hussy!\N– No! I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Tsubaki, stop it!\N– Please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear... He's uncontrollable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:43.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Tsubaki is so rough.\N– No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:45.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Although, it seems you'll need...\N– I said sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– practice on taming your power.\N– Please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:51.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:59.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going to\Nthe Soul Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:20.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was the fifth Encroachment\Njust ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:25.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they repeat the cycle of\Nseveral minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of Encroachment and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,During the Encroachment of the chain,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:35.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move because it's\Nso painful I could go blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:40.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to act while they're asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That kid makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:57.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The method is reckless,\Nbut he's managing to climb
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,about three meters of this\Nvirtually straight-up wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my my...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:04.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:12.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:15.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you getting hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:20.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!\NBesides, I'm in a soul form!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:22.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I get hungry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:26.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's good! I'll tell you\Nsomething interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:30.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When you get feeling hungry\Nwhile in soul form...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it's a dangerous sign,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:34.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that you're just a step away\Nfrom becoming a Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:38.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to feel thirsty, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:42.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And if you do get thirsty,\Ngo ahead and drink my spit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here... Ururu... You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:46.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on down! Hey you! Brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:51.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:54.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Stop!\NI'll beat the crap outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:57.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:21.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's dark outside...\NIt's hard to tell the time in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I can't climb it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:33.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How much time has passed?\NI can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:37.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How can I climb outta this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:55.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you some food.\NI figured you'd start feeling hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:58.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:01.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd get hungry!\NTake a good look...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:04.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's still quite a few links\Nto the Chain of Fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:09.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can't be helped
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:11.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,if you can't tell time in\Na place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:18.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,70 hours have passed since\Nyou came down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Some quick ones start turning\Ninto Hollows already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:26.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Also one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:31.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The final Encroachment\Nis nothing like the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:32.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:38.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-All the chains...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:44.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All of you! Sto--!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:24.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey! He's going to become\Na Hollow, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going into rescue mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:29.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Watch him carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:37.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, when a Plus\Nbecomes a Hollow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:40.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the spiritual body first explodes,\Nand then reforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in his case, the order is all mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:48.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The body is still a Plus,\Nwhile the mask is being created first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:51.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is proof that he is resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:56.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a possibility that\Nhe will become a Soul Reaper again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's watch a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And see if he truly becomes a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:51.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:55.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:56.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:06.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It still can't reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:14.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must I cry out\Nbefore you can hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:19.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one in this world that\Nknows me better than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:22.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:27.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I don't know anyone\Ndepressing like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:32.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:42.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised. How can you stay\Nseated in a place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:53.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you can scream,\NI guess you have time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a good sign. Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:14:00.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers rule death.\NThey control many spiritual beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:05.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...not...a Soul Reaper now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:10.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Remember! That the Soul Reaper power\Nthat Byakuya Kuchiki snuffed out of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:15.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,was merely the Soul Reaper power\Nyou received from Rukia Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:20.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! That is all he was after.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:25.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He thought that by destroying that,\Nhe could end this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:35.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He overlooked the fact that you have\NSoul Reaper power of your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:41.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My own? Soul Reaper power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:48.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The power that was awakening\Ndue to Rukia Kuchiki's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hid itself in the very depths\Nof your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,an instant before Byakuya Kuchiki's thrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If there ever is a time when
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you could find the power of\Nthe Soul Reaper that has hidden itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:07.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then that time is now,\Nwhen this world has begun its collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:11.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Countless boxes are raining down,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:16.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and in only one of them lies\Nyour Soul Reaper power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you cut out\Nthis nonsense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:26.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will not abide any excuses.\NThere is no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:31.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Before this world is\Ncompletely destroyed, find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:34.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or you will become a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How can I pick out\None box out of all these,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:50.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that contains the Soul Reaper power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:16:01.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't have the ability to\Nsearch for spiritual energy to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:06.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think Ishida said\Nthe same thing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:08.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:13.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...how did he find out\NI was a Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:16.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was some simple method...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:23.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He bragged about it...\Nbut what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:26.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Spirit Ribbon of\Na Soul Reaper is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the---?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:52.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The handle of a Zanpaku-to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've done well in finding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:06.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that next time,\Nyou will hear my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could you possibly be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NIt's crumbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:20.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and pull me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:22.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:43.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the limit, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:46.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am switching to Suppression mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:51.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo 99 Part 2: Ban-kin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:54.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,First Incantation: Bandage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Second Incantation: Hundred Dead Bolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:04.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Tessai!\NIf you do that, he'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is no other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:09.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold him down any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I must destroy him before\Nhe becomes a Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:18.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Final Incantation: Fatal Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:27.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:32.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:49.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:01.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:02.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Answer, Orange head!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:08.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you're alive, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:12.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:23.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shihakusho...and a mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a Hollow? Or a Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take me lightly!\NCome at us if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:58.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't become a Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:12.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You went and became\Na Soul Reaper again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:14.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well done! Lesson Two cleared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:24.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Your number is up now\Nthat I came back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:31.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I swore! That when I got out\Nof the hole alive, I'd kill you without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:42.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With that spirit,\Nwe'll go right into Lesson Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lesson Three has\Nno time limit at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:51.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you can use your Zanpaku-to\Nto knock off my hat,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then the lesson will be cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:04.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, considering\Nyour Zanpaku-to is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:10.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! And I haven't really gotten\Ndown to business yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:14.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No time limit, huh?\NForget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's end this in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:22.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:26.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll end this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:46.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:49.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:52.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:54.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:56.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:58.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:00.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:03.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was casually walking through town
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time dusk fell\Nand the city was bathed in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:08.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was an afternoon with\Ncrowds of people coming and going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:10.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why but\NI just stood there and watched
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:12.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then my cell phone started to vibrate\Nand I made myself move
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:14.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hoping it could fill\Nin this hole in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not alone\NYou see, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:18.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hold each other up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:21.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:23.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:26.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:28.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:30.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:32.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:35.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:38.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to release the power\Nof the Zanpaku-to,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:41.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,one has to discover\Nits name and summon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.26,0:22:46.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, can Ichigo find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,1000 points says he can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:49.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,2000 points says I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:49.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...